General.Name: Master Pack Group Bhd
General.Description: Master-Pack Group Berhad, an investment holding company, manufactures, distributes, and sells corrugated cartons and wooden packaging materials in Malaysia, Vietnam, and internationally. It offers sheet board, slotted type, telescope type, folder type, interior fitment, die-cut, and palletized shipping container products. The company also provides other packaging materials, including PE form, PU form, corrupad, cushion pad, edge protector, air bubble bag, plastic bag, strapping band, newsprint paper, and bubble pack products; manufactures and sells paper bags, laminated hawker papers, and laminated corrugated paper containers or paper lunch boxes; and manufactures and trades in wood packaging boxes. In addition, it is involved in property letting activities. The company was formerly known as Hunza Consolidation Berhad and changed its name to Master-Pack Group Berhad in June 2009. Master-Pack Group Berhad was incorporated in 1994 and is based in Nibong Tebal, Malaysia.
